release_note: Stability improvement

Compatibility improvement Recent updates: Image : Added the Image option. Pro version allows up to 9 images Free version allows 1 image. After adding an image you can preview save or share it. Long press on the preview screen to add a frame. Location : Added the Location option. Click to include various location information and coordinates. Inspiration : Introduced the Inspiration option. Now you can select inspirational sentences and diary themes in Chinese English or Japanese randomly generated to ignite your creativity. Export : Included additional export formats. Pro version supports PDF Encrypted PDF PNG Image TXT and CSV while the Free version supports TXT CSV and DOCX. Font Size : When adjusting the font size the specific size will be displayed in real time on the right side of the title. Custom Toolbar : Removed the previous simplified mode. In the appearance settings you can now customize the toolbar by sorting or deleting unnecessary icons. Enjoy full customization. Main App Icon : Replaced the main app icon however you can still use the original one if desired. Resolved occasional issue of duplicate diary generation. Enhanced performance stability and localization.
